    "description": "The toggle will switch each time the top rail is pulsed `N` times, where `N` is the number of items in the dropper counter below. Same concept as https://discord.com/channels/1375556143186837695/1386448150994223134/1386448150994223134 but can switch faster, at 8gt clock input if needed.",
